snippet.title: De De Pyaar De 2 - Official Trailer | Ajay Devgn, R. Madhavan, Rakul Preet, Meezaan Jafri | 14th Nov
snippet.description:
In De De Pyaar De 2, love faces its toughest test yet as Ashish visits Ayesha‚Äôs family home!
Will the age-gap romance win hearts or stir things up? With heart, humour and a whole lot of family madness, this Pyaar vs Parivaar clash promises a relatable, riotous ride for every kind of audience.

De De Pyaar De 2 is directed by Anshul Sharma, produced by T-Series‚Äô Bhushan Kumar & Krishan Kumar, and Luv Films‚Äô Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg. The film is set to release in cinemas on 14th November 2025.

Presenting the Energetic teaser of #AndhraKingTaluka 

Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is a Telugu Film starring Ram Pothineni, Upendra and Bhagyashri Borse. The film is written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. The film brings untold emotions between a fan and a superstar onto the big screens on 28th November worldwide.

snippet.title: KRAMP Trailer | Kiran Abbavaraam | Yukti Thareja | Jains Nani | Razesh Danda | Hasya Movies
snippet.description:
KRAMP Trailer on Hasya Movies.

KRAMP is an Upcoming 2025 Telugu Movie Starring Kiran Abbavaraam, Yukti Thareja & Others. Directed by Jains Nani. Music by Chaitan Bharadwaj. Produced by Razesh Danda under Hasya Movies Banner and Shiva Bommak under Ruudransh Celluloid. The film is set to release in theaters this Diwali on October 18, 2025.

snippet.title: YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video)
snippet.description:
YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video)

Listen now: https://DESITRILL.lnk.to/YUNGSAMMY-MUDDA

YUNG SAMMY says ‚ÄúMUDDA‚Äù ain‚Äôt just a word, it‚Äôs an issue, a problem, a whole storm. When me and Seedhe Maut hit the studio, every line we wrote was about the scene, the hustle, the chaos. It‚Äôs called ‚ÄúMUDDA‚Äù ‚Äôcause when YUNG SAMMY and Seedhe Maut jump on a track, it‚Äôs not just music, it‚Äôs a warning. It‚Äôs trouble, it‚Äôs ruckus, it‚Äôs pressure on the whole game. We went all in, no filter, real talk straight from the hood. Turning struggles into flex, pain into power. ‚ÄúMUDDA‚Äù is an anthem, a rager, an energy you can‚Äôt ignore. This is heavyweight talk, facts only.‚Äù

Lyrics: 
ENCORE VERSE
Seedhe Maut Sammy hai, dikhta bas grey
Chai pe baithe hum London ya Noida
Lulli si shakal ka, bhidenge hum se
Hum rapper complete hai jaise Cu Boi ka
Hona jo waise bhi ho gaya
Tu toh pitega par bol kya karenge tere boy ka
Sona tha bandi ke chucho mein
Lekin vo aaj ki raat se khabar pe soyega
Kha kise kitno ki maa chodi x2
Aah ahh
Kamar se nikala ghoda aur bandi ko
Diya bana ghodi
Aah
Muh chodni karte hai baalak
Aur baalak aa karte hai muh chodi
Shakle dikhte hain news akhbaaron mein
Jaise main hoon Modi ooh ooh

Calm (1st Verse)
Kaha par hain rapper, ye dikhte nahi, gaayab hain
Dost inke SM pe flip ho rahi
Janwar hain baithe, teen rapper nahi
Papa hu ladko ka, chhaate mein chup ho rahe
Ye mic pe chilla rahe par inke ye jhaate se vocal nahi clip ho rahe, na na
Ye paisa, ye bitches, ye bud hai kamaaya
Bas music se, fatah bin filmon ke
Haan Greater Noida wala shit hai, saath hai Sammy jo
Ek bandi mujhko boli Calm se bajna hai, don‚Äôt say no
Main jau jaha paisa jaye, jab launde jaaye jaha booty go
If the truth be told, yaha dono ladke nuke hain, phod

Yung Sammy (1st Verse)
Yung Sammy aur Seedhe Maut, dekh bhai gaand toh tutni hai
Bhari rakha poora system, ab life lage meri movie hai
I‚Äôm one of a kind aur bitch meri lage mujhe kaafi choosy hai
Ek bandi ho rahi mujhse kaafi frank, mere sar pe chadh ke khud rahi hai
Verse likha maine UK mein, par Delhi mein jaake ye take liya
Kaafi pehle se tha studio mein locked in, fir LA mein jaake ek break liya
Don‚Äôt give a fuck about a price tag, mera maan kiya toh phir le liya
Ek beti chod ka faltu bol raha, gaadi ki dikki mein ghar diya
Marta tha bunk mein business classes
But now I fly that shit
Teacher jo kehti thi ‚Äútu likhta nahi achha‚Äù
She knows I write that shit
Har ek baar mera holy verse
Jaise karta hoon main baptizing
Don‚Äôt give a f*** about a b*** ego
Aur karta nahi kabhi main backbiting

YUNG SAMMY & SEEDHE MAUT Verse
Yung Sammy, SM, yaha pe koi rakhna nahi pair, it‚Äôs a landmine ting (CALM)
Na chale koi branding, na chale marketing, na chale franchise (ENCORE)
Bata kaise na tutegi gaand ab inki, jab
Bacha koi chaara hi nahi 

YUNG SAMMY
Bata kaise na sukhengi praan, inke baap
Se hai bane koi sayana nahi, bitch 
ENCORE
Mere gang mein cheete hi cheete, aur
Kabhi bhi saapon ko paala hi nahi 
YUNG SAMMY
Likhu jab bhi lage jaise jaan aayi nayi
Beaton pe main chadhun jaise baadh aayi kahin 
CALM
Bags and bags and bags, damn
Khoke se niche toh aata hi nahi
Apno se pada tera paala hi nahi
Gandhi toh tune kabhi chaapa hi nahi
Abey haat 
YUNG SAMMY
Leta hoon main halke mein, tumhe toh bil mein raho
Sher abhi dahda hai nahi
Bhussi bharu chahiye mujhe chaar line hi
Aisa koi bhi din nahi jab ye maal aaye nahi 
CALM
Kholu tera sar jaise taala yahi daala
Tere sar pe main maala, pade thai thai
Galat hue tere haalat yahi
Tera MUDDA banega aaj raat yahi 
ENCORE
